              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>《美学散步》是一代宗师宗白华先生汇集了一生最精要的美学篇章也是先生生前唯一的一部美学著作。 </p><p> 诗（文学）和画的分界</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p45229581-3.jpg"></div></div><p>十八世纪德国古代艺术史学者温克尔曼在他的早期著作《关于绘画和雕刻艺术里模仿希腊作品的一些意见》里曾有下列一段论希腊雕刻的名句：</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p45229581-4.jpg"></div></div><p>对于希腊雕像群拉奥孔温克尔曼认为：</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p45229581-5.jpg"></div></div><p>十八世纪德国思想家莱辛发表了他的美学著作〈拉奥孔或论画和诗的分界〉</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p45229581-6.jpg"></div></div><p>莱辛在〈拉奥孔或论画和诗的分界〉里说：</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p45229581-10.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p45229581-8.jpg"></div></div><p></p><p>唐朝诗人王昌龄有一首诗〈初日〉</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p45229581-11.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">P11页</div></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p45229581-12.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">P12页</div></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p45229581-2.jpg"></div></div><p>本章结尾</p><div class="image-con